    [python] Fix error when running dev server on a django project. (#15483)
    
    When starting a WSGI app using `vercel dev`, `BaseWSGIServer.__init__`
    will attempt to get the version via `importlib.metadata.version`.
    However, since `django` does not depend on `werkzeug` there is no
    `.dist-info` to look up a version.
    
    `vercel dev` uses a vendored copy of `werkzeug`, but that does not
    provide a `.dist-info`. Instead of using `importlib`, this PR adds a
    function to read `vendor.txt` and extract the specific version used.

